title: Extent to which U.S. was dominated by consensus

content.question:
While the United States appeared to be dominated by consensus and conformity in the 1950s, some Americans reacted against the status quo.
Analyze the critiques of United States society made by TWO of the following.

Youth
Civil Rights Activists
Intellectuals
